<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Add JDK for your project</b></p><p>You can add JDK of the required version and vendor right from the IDE. Go to <span class="control">File | Project Structure | Project</span>, expand the <span class="control">SDK</span> list, and select <span class="control">Download JDK</span>. This option is also available for new projects in the <span class="control">New Project</span> wizard (<span class="control">File | New | Project</span>).</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_add_jdk.png" alt="Adding JDK" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>